        </div>
        
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-expand-arrows-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Scalability</h3>
            <p>Scale your SEO services up or down based on client demand without hiring staff.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Expertise On-Demand</h3>
            <p>Access seasoned SEO professionals who live and breathe search algorithms.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Brand Consistency</h3>
            <p>All deliverables carry your brand, maintaining client relationships under your name.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-piggy-bank"></i>
            </div>
