            <p>Get expert SEO services at a fraction of the cost of hiring in-house specialists.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Scenario Example -->
  <section class="scenario-section">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="scenario-card">
        <div class="scenario-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="scenario-content">
          <h3>Imagine This Scenario:</h3>
          <p>You run a web design or marketing agency in London, and one of your clients asks if you can help improve their Google rankings. Rather than turning them away or scrambling to learn SEO overnight, you can say "Yes, we can!" With our reseller SEO services, you'll have a dedicated team of SEO experts working on that client's campaign.</p>
