      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits for Digital Agencies -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Benefits of Our White Label SEO Services <span>for Digital Agencies</span></h2>
        <p>Partnering with a white label SEO provider like Bright Forge SEO gives your business a competitive edge. Here are some key benefits agencies and entrepreneurs enjoy when using our white label SEO services:</p>
      </div>
      
