        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Cost-Effective Growth</h3>
          <p>Hiring full-time SEO specialists or consultants can be expensive. Outsourcing to our team in the Philippines is cost-efficient you get high-quality work at a fraction of the cost of hiring locally. This means better margins for your agency and affordable packages for your clients.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Access Expert Talent</h3>
          <p>SEO is our bread and butter. By reselling our services, you tap into a team of seasoned SEO experts who live and breathe search engine algorithms, content strategy, and link building. We stay on top of industry trends, so you don't have to.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Focus On Your Core Business</h3>
          <p>Spend your time on what you do best whether it's account management, design, or other marketing services while we handle the nitty-gritty of SEO. No more stretching yourself thin trying to master every aspect of digital marketing. We've got the SEO covered so you can focus on growing your business.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Scalable And Flexible</h3>
