        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Your Brand, Our Work</h3>
          <p>Everything we do is delivered under your brand. We provide white-labelled reports and updates with your logo and branding if needed. To your clients, it appears that all the work was done by your in-house team. You maintain full ownership of client relationships and credit for results, strengthening your brand reputation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Philippines Section -->
  <section class="philippines-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>White Label SEO Services in the Philippines <span>Why It Makes Sense</span></h2>
