      </div>
      
      <div class="philippines-grid">
        <div class="philippines-card">
          <div class="philippines-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-globe-americas"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Highly Skilled, English-Proficient Team</h3>
          <p>The Philippines is home to talented SEO professionals who are fluent in English and familiar with Western markets. This means no language barriers and content that resonates with your client's audience. Our team's expertise comes from handling campaigns for various industries and regions, giving us the experience to drive results in competitive markets.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="philippines-card">
          <div class="philippines-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Cost Advantages Without Compromise</h3>
          <p>Operating in the Philippines allows us to deliver top-notch SEO services at lower costs. You benefit from pricing that keeps you competitive without sacrificing quality. It's the reason so many agencies worldwide look for white label SEO services in the Philippines you get more value for your money.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="philippines-card">
          <div class="philippines-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Reliability And Work Ethic</h3>
          <p>Filipino professionals are known for their dedication and hard work. We take deadlines seriously and go the extra mile to meet campaign goals. When we commit to a project, we treat it as our own with meticulous attention to detail and a passion for seeing your clients succeed.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="philippines-card">
          <div class="philippines-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Timezone Advantage For Global Coverage</h3>
          <p>Our team can work while you sleep. Being in a different timezone (GMT+8) often means we're busy implementing changes and optimisations during your off-hours. By the time you start your day, you'll usually have updates and progress reports waiting for you. It's like having a 24/7 operation without the added complexity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="philippines-summary">
        <p>As a result of these advantages, we've become a trusted partner for agencies seeking SEO services in the Philippines. Bright Forge SEO combines the best of both worlds: world-class expertise and affordable service. You and your clients benefit from a leading SEO team working from one of the most outsourcing-friendly locations on the planet.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our White Label SEO Solutions -->
  <section class="solutions-section" id="services">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our White Label SEO Solutions <span>What We Deliver</span></h2>
        <p>When you partner with Bright Forge SEO, you gain access to a full suite of SEO services that cover everything your clients need to rank higher and drive organic traffic. We don't do half-measures our reseller SEO services are comprehensive and tailored to each client's goals. Here's what our white label SEO team can handle for you:</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="solutions-grid">
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>White Label SEO Audits & Technical Optimisation</h3>
          <p>Our team performs comprehensive white label SEO audits for your clients, uncovering key ranking opportunities, fixing site structure issues, and resolving technical SEO problems. From schema markup to mobile performance, we ensure the site is 100% search-engine friendly.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-key"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Keyword Research & Strategy</h3>
          <p>Our team researches the keywords and search terms that matter most to your client's business. We analyse search volumes, competition, and user intent to create a targeted keyword strategy. This way, your client's content is optimised for the terms their customers are actually searching for.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-edit"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>On-Page Optimisation</h3>
          <p>We fine-tune website content and HTML elements for SEO best practices. This includes crafting compelling title tags and meta descriptions, using header tags correctly, improving content structure, and ensuring keywords are naturally integrated. The result is a site that search engines understand, and users love to browse.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-pen-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Content Creation & SEO Copywriting</h3>
          <p>Great content is at the heart of great SEO. Our copywriters produce high-quality, SEO-friendly content such as blog posts, product descriptions, landing page copy, and more all tailored to your client's brand voice. If your client already has a content team, we can guide and optimise their writers.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
          </div>
