        </div>
        
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Local SEO & Google Business Optimisation</h3>
          <p>If your client serves local customers, we'll optimise their Google My Business profile and regional listings, manage reviews, and ensure they appear in local search results and maps. From localised content to citation building, we help your clients become more visible to customers in their area.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Regular Reporting & Analytics</h3>
          <p>Stay in the loop with detailed, white-labelled reports that showcase progress. We provide monthly (or even weekly) SEO reports highlighting key metrics like rankings, organic traffic, and conversions. Each report can carry your agency's branding. We're also happy to hop on review calls (behind the scenes or anonymously) to help you interpret results and plan next steps for your client's campaign.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="solution-card">
          <div class="solution-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Custom SEO Solutions</h3>
          <p>Don't see a specific SEO service listed? Just ask! Our goal is to act as a valid extension of your team, so we tailor our services to fit what your client needs. From e-commerce SEO to technical migrations, if it's within the realm of SEO, chances are we've got you covered.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Partner With Us -->
  <section class="partner-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Partner With <span>Bright Forge SEO?</span></h2>
        <p>We know that when it comes to choosing a white label SEO partner, you have options. Here's what sets Bright Forge SEO apart and why agencies trust us with their clients' SEO.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="partner-content">
        <div class="partner-features">
          <div class="partner-feature">
            <div class="partner-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="partner-text">
              <h3>Proven Expertise & Experience</h3>
              <p>Our team is made up of SEO specialists with years of experience achieving top rankings for clients in various industries. We're not newbies or generalists we're specialists in SEO. When you work with us, you're tapping into a wealth of knowledge.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="partner-feature">
            <div class="partner-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="partner-text">
              <h3>Transparent, Data-Driven Approach</h3>
              <p>At Bright Forge SEO, we believe in transparency. You'll always know what we're doing for your clients and why. We use data and analytics to drive our SEO strategy, and we share those insights with you. No smoke and mirrors just honest work and clear results.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="partner-feature">
            <div class="partner-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="partner-text">
              <h3>White Hat Methods Only</h3>
              <p>Your clients' websites are safe in our hands. We strictly employ white hat SEO techniques that align with Google's guidelines. That means no spammy shortcuts or risky tactics that could harm rankings in the long run. Our focus is on sustainable, long-term growth for your clients' sites.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="partner-feature">
            <div class="partner-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="partner-text">
              <h3>Seamless Communication & Support</h3>
              <p>Consider us an extension of your team. We keep communication open and can adapt to your preferred workflow. Need an update on a campaign or have a question from your client? We're quick to respond and provide detailed answers. We can even help you prepare for client meetings by supplying talking points or joining calls as an "invisible" SEO consultant if necessary.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="partner-feature">
            <div class="partner-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="partner-text">
              <h3>Reliable & On-Time Delivery</h3>
              <p>Deadlines and commitments matter to us. When we agree on a timeline or campaign plan, we stick to it. You can rely on us to deliver reports, content pieces, and optimisations on schedule, helping you maintain your reputation for reliability with your clients.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="partner-summary">
          <p>By partnering with Bright Forge SEO, you gain a trusted ally invested in your agency's success. We take pride in helping you shine to your clients. After all, when your clients see great SEO results, it reflects well on you and that's our ultimate goal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ContactSection />
  <Footer slot="footer" />
